f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umkondr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mkondr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/24/02 11:58:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> Hey guys!<br>I have been invited to go to a PoG raid this week.  I am wondering is it worth it to ruin my ally Tunare faction for rogue armor that drops there.  To determine if it is worth it, I would like someone to post the statistics of the Rogue Armor in PoG.  Would be real cool if you can post stats as a responce, instead of posting a link as I have issues accessing some sites.  Thanks a lot for your responce,<br><br>Lileden Shadowbane<br>Redeemed and Epified Blackguard of 56 Season <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=fluxus>Fluxus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/24/02 12:18:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> Assassin's Boots  +18 AC +5 Sta +3 Agi +20 HP <br><br>Assassin's Bracer  +13 AC +2 Str +4 Sta +15 HP<br> <br>Assassin's Chain Leggings  +22 AC +10 Str +4 Agi +4 Dex +1 vsMg +1 vsFire +1 vsCold +1 vsPos +1 vsDis +60 HP<br><br>Assassin's Chain Sleeves  +16 AC +7 Dex +3 vsMg +2 vsDis +25 HP<br><br>Assassin's Chestguard  +37 AC +10 Str +7 Sta +14 Agi +7 Dex +7 vsMg +3 vsFire +60 HP  Effect: Invigorate <br><br>Assassin's Coif  +16 AC +4 Str +3 Agi +3 Dex +2 vsMg +3 vsPos +15 HP <br><br>Assassin's Gauntlets  +13 AC +3 Str +1 Sta +3 Agi +1 Dex +2 vsMg <br><br><br>There ya go. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umkondr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mkondr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/24/02 1:19:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> Holy cow man!<br><br>I was thinking it is something like Hate drops, but this is way better.  I am so going to PoG.  Thanks a lot for your help.<br><br>Lileden Shadowbane<br>Redeemed and Epified Blackguard of 56 Seasons <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugnix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gnix</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/24/02 4:55:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> You can see how this compares to other available velious armor on our ezboard here:<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub8.ezboard.com/flotuscultresources.showMessage?topicID=87.topic">pub8.ezboard.com/flotuscu...D=87.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uimmutablemutation.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Immutable Mutation</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/25/02 3:36:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> Thurg is easier to get, and drops a hell of a lot more often. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uchianaxev.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ChianaXev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/25/02 3:47:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> Giants don't drop tons of gems, though.<br><br>I found it faster to collect gems in pog and buy thurg MQ's than to get drops in Kael.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umkondr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mkondr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/25/02 4:27:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11628.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Armor in PoG</span><hr size=1> I don't know guys, in 56 (almost 57) levels of fighting, I have yet to see a single piece of rogue chain dropping in Kael.  I have been on countless for